<p>This week in <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp99.mp3">SmallBizPod #99</a>, Jane Tchan, editor of SmallBizPod, interviews Tanya Wheway, chairman of Wheway Lifestyle International on how she and her husband became pioneers of the modern health farm movement and went on to build an international consultancy and management services company. She also gives advice on how to take the stress out of running a business.</p>
<p>Right click <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp99.mp3">here</a> to download the podcast for start-ups, small businesses and entrepreneurs.</p>
