9 01:55:12 PST</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/?p=1235</guid><content:encoded xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><![CDATA[<div class="tweetmeme_button" style="margin-left: 3px;">
			<a href="http://api.tweetmeme.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.smallbizpod.co.uk%2F2009%2F11%2F12%2Fsmallbizpod-92-web-startups-shooting-for-the-moon-or-nailing-the-business-model%2F"><br />
				<img src="http://api.tweetmeme.com/imagebutton.gif?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.smallbizpod.co.uk%2F2009%2F11%2F12%2Fsmallbizpod-92-web-startups-shooting-for-the-moon-or-nailing-the-business-model%2F&amp;source=smallbiztweets&amp;style=compact&amp;service=bit.ly&amp;b=2" height="61" width="50" /><br />
