<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp89.mp3">SmallBizPod #89</a>, the podcast for startups and small businesses, features an interview Jill Sutherland, co-founder of award-winning sandwich shop, Taste, on being successful as an independent retailer in recession.</p>
