<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp88.mp3">SmallBizPod #88</a>, the small business advice  podcast, includes an interview with Alex Will and Henry Erskine Crum, the two young web entrepreneurs behind <a href="http://www.spoonfed.co.uk">Spoonfed</a>, an events, listings and review site that looks set to challenge Time Out and create a new model for online publishing and event marketing.</p>
<p>Right click <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp88.mp3">here</a> to download the podcast for start-ups, small businesses and entrepreneurs.</p>
