<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp87.mp3">SmallBizPod #87</a>, the startups podcast, looks at the tips and tricks of launching an eBay business and how existing businesses can make the most of the auction site as an online sales channel.  Includes interviews with two leading experts, <a href="http://www.wilsondan.co.uk">Dan Wilson</a> and Sue Bailey of <a href="http://www.tamebay.com/">tamebay.com</a>.</p>
<p>Right click <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp87.mp3">here</a> to download the podcast for start-ups, small businesses and entrepreneurs.</p>
