<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp83.mp3">SmallBizPod #83</a>, the small business podcast, includes an interview with young entrepreneur, Duane Jackson, the controversial founder of Kashflow the accountancy software as a service business.  There&#8217;s also an open air review of the book Leap! by Ian Sanders and a musical surprise.</p>
