<p>Features:</p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">&#9679;</span> 01:53 Thanks to <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.xlntelecom.co.uk/?affl=sbpod">XLN Telecom</a> for sponsoring the podcast.  Please support SmallBizPod by supporting our sponsors.</p>
