<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">&#9679;</span> 02:17 <strong>Interview</strong> with Duane Jackson, founder of <a href="http://www.kashflow.co.uk/" rel="nofollow">Kashflow</a> on how a ZX Spectrum and later support from The Prince&#8217;s Trust helped him overcome early setbacks to create a successful and innovative software business.  Alex and Duane also talk about PR, controversy, the challenge of larger competitors and what Duane has learned about business on an extraorindary entrepreneurial journey.</p>
