<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp82.mp3">SmallBizPod #82</a>, the small business podcast, covers the 2009 Budget, analysing its impact on startups, small businesses and entrepreneurs.  It includes interviews with startups, SMEs, experts and shadow ministers for business and enterprise for the Conservatives and the Lib Dems.  There&#8217;s also an excellent review of a book on coaching from an Australian listener and some classic electronica.</p>
<p>Right click <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp82.mp3">here</a> to download the podcast for start-ups, small business and entrepreneurs.</p>
