<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp81.mp3">SmallBizPod #81</a>, the small business podcast, includes a great interview with Laura Tenison, the female entrepreneur behind maternity and toddler retail fashion business <a href="http://www.jojomamanbebe.co.uk/" rel="nofollow" >JoJo Maman B&#233;b&#233;</a>.  There&#8217;s also a round-up of listener comments, an interview with a Scottish entrepreneur who is big in Japan and some great music thanks to Monotonik.</p>
<p>Right click <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp81.mp3">here</a> to download the podcast for startups, small business owners and entrepreneurs.</p>
