<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp80.mp3">SmallBizPod #80</a>, the podcast for startups and entrepreneurs, focuses on franchising with an interview with the godfather of British hairdressing and business brand legend, Toni Mascolo, founder of Toni &#038; Guy, and an interview with Atul Pathak, one of McDonald&#8217;s most successful franchisees.  With thanks to the British Library&#8217;s Business and IP Centre.</p>
<p>Right click <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp80.mp3">here</a> to download the podcast for startups, small business and entrepreneurs.</p>
