<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp78.mp3">SmallBizPod #78</a>, the podcast for startups and entrepreneurs, kicks off the new year with a positive interview with Irish entrepreneurship expert and motivational speaker, Kevin Kelly.  The focus of the podcast is on creating a positive outlook, customers and sales in the tough environment of 2009.  There&#8217;s also another listener book review and details of SmallBizPod Sevens.</p>
<p>Right click <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp78.mp3">here</a> to download the podcast for startups, small business and entrepreneurs.</p>
<p><strong>Click on the play button below to listen now</strong></p>
