<p><strong>Summary</strong></p>
<p>Intro:</p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">•</span> 00:00 Introduction to what&#8217;s coming up in the show.<br />
<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">•</span> 01:24 A big thank you to new sponsors <a href="http://www.alibaba.com/?src=ibdm_d02p0081e02r03">Alibaba.com</a>.<br />
