<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp73.mp3">SmallBizPod #73</a>, the entrepreneurs&#8217; podcast, includes a series of inspiring interviews on social entrepreneurship at an extraordinary three day event called <a href="http://shineunconference.com/">Shine</a> which took place in May 2008.  There&#8217;s also the first audio review of a business book by listener Peter Henderson and comments from other listeners too.</p>
<p>Right click <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp73.mp3">here</a> to download the podcast for startups, small business and entrepreneurs.</p>
