<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp71.mp3">SmallBizPod #71</a>, interviews Alastair Mitchell, ceo and co-founder of successful UK Web 2.0 startup <a href="http://www.huddle.net/">Huddle</a>, on building a business on the web, angel funding and dealing with competition. There&#8217;s also the usual round up of comments, an update on the book review challenge and another gorgeous electronica track.</p>
<p>Right click <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp71.mp3">here</a> to download the podcast for startups, small business and entrepreneurs.</p>
