<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp70.mp3">SmallBizPod #70</a>, includes interviews with Gitanjali Banerjee Bhattacharya and Kaustav Bhattacharya about their plans for <a href="http://www.jagritiyatra.com">Jagriti Yatra</a>, an inspiring entrepreneurial train journey across India, and what it hopes to achieve. There&#8217;s also the usual round up of comments, books for review and a beautiful track from the Bombay Dub Orchestra.</p>
