<p><strong>Show Notes</strong></p>
<p><strong>Summary</strong></p>
<p>Intro:</p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial">•</span> 00:00 Introduction to what&#8217;s coming up in the show.<br />
<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial">•</span> 01:17 Check out the latest episode of <a href="http://www.bizpodtv.com">BizPod TV</a>.<br />
