<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp69.mp3">SmallBizPod #69</a>, the small business podcast, includes an interview with Clive Birnie, managing director of <a href="http://www.severndelta.co.uk">Severn Delta</a>, on his experiences of a successful management buy-out, funding, leadership, blogging and much more. There&#8217;s also the announcement of the winners of the Rachel Elnaugh book competition and the chance to win tickets to <a href="http://fuel-conference.com/speakers">Fuel</a>. </p>
