<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp68.mp3">SmallBizPod #68</a>, the podcast for startups and business owners, interviews Rachel Elnaugh, former &#8216;Dragon&#8217; and one of Britain&#8217;s best known entrepreneurs. There&#8217;s also a round up of comments from listeners and a chance to win Rachel&#8217;s new book <a href="http://www.rachelelnaugh.co.uk/business-nightmares">Business Nightmares</a>.</p>
<p>Right click <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp68.mp3">here</a> to download the podcast for startups, small business and entrepreneurs.</p>
