<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp66.mp3">SmallBizPod #66</a>, the podcast for startups and entrepreneurs, includes an in depth interview with Dan Harple, founder and ceo of mobile lifestyle application, <a href="http://www.gypsii.com/">GyPSii</a>. A fascinating insight into tech entrepreneurship and the mobile web.</p>
<p>Right click <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp66.mp3">here</a> to download the podcast for startups, small business and entrepreneurs.</p>
<p><strong>Click on the play button below to listen now</strong></p>
