<p>Intro:</p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial">•</span> 00:00 Alex on what&#8217;s coming up in the show.<br />
<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial">•</span> 01:08 Do check out a new small business TV  podcast aimed at startups and entrepreneurs &#8211; <a href="http://www.bizpodtv.com">BizPod TV</a>.  Subscribe to this business video podcast on <a href="http://phobos.apple.com/WebObjects/MZStore.woa/wa/viewPodcast?id=275753851">iTunes</a>.<br />
