<p>Features: </p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial">•</span> 03:00 <strong>Interview</strong> with David Wei, chief executive officer of <a href="http://www.alibaba.com/">Alibaba.com</a> the international online market place for small and medium-sized enterprises.  David and Alex discuss, alibaba.com&#8217;s successful conversion from start-up to successful IPO, the company&#8217;s brand, ethos and how it maintains its small business grass roots and original entrepreneurial essence. They also talk about how the internet has flattened the world to the benefit of SMEs, the issue of pollution in China and tips for success in trading with Chinese companies.</p>
