<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp62.mp3">SmallBizPod #62</a>, the small business podcast, takes a look at social enterprise and social firms in particular.  Inspiring interviews with social entrepreneurs include: Nigel Kershaw, chairman of <a href="http://www.bigissue.com/">The Big Issue</a>, Sally Reynold, ceo of <a href="http://www.socialfirms.co.uk/">Social Firms UK</a> and Jenny Sims, ceo of <a href="http://www.pembrokeshire-frame.org.uk/">Pembrokeshire FRAME</a>.</p>
<p>Right click <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp62.mp3">here</a> to download the podcast for startup, small business and entrepreneurs.</p>
