<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp57.mp3">SmallBizPod #57</a>, the small business advice podcast, includes an interview with, Will King, CEO of <a href="http://www.shave.com/">King of Shaves</a> about how he took his shaving products business from £300 sales and a £30,000 loss in year one, to a brand with international ambitions which is already snapping at the heals of market leader Gillette in the UK.</p>
