<p>Intro:</p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial">•</span> 00:00 Alex on what&#8217;s coming up in the show.<br />
<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial">•</span> 00:57 If you have a moment, please take the <a href="http://www.surveymonkey.com/s.aspx?sm=AcxFiYP_2bHSuORjmDOMX_2b_2fQ_3d_3d">SmallBizPod survey</a> and you could win an iPod Touch.<br />
