<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial">• </span> 32.07 Diarmuid O&#8217;Donovan writes to mention that <a href="http://www.cpdwise.com">cpdwise.com</a> has been nominated Ireland&#8217;s <a href="http://www.netvisionary.ie/vote2007.html">Net Visionary Awards</a>.  Check out the site and give him a vote!<br />
<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial">• </span> 32.34 Thanks from Andrea for advice for her property letting business in Barcelona.<br />
<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial">• </span> 32.53 Thanks to Gordon Graham who writes a great <a href="http://orxilinasia.blogspot.com/">blog on innovation</a> and creates some excellent progressive house mixes!<br />
