<p>If you can spare 5-10 minutes and are a regular listener to the podcast or reader of the blog, I&#8217;d be very grateful if you&#8217;d take part in a short online survey on SmallBizPod.</p>
<p>It really is only 5-10 minutes to do and there aren&#8217;t any hard questions!</p>
<p>And like all good surveys, it comes with an incentive <img src='http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_wink.gif' alt=';)' class='wp-smiley' />  Click <a href="http://www.surveymonkey.com/s.aspx?sm=AcxFiYP_2bHSuORjmDOMX_2b_2fQ_3d_3d">here</a> or on the iPod Touch image on the right hand side of this page to begin.</p>
<p>Thanks for your time and support.</p>
