.co.uk)</dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 17 Sep 2007 05:36:25 PDT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/2007/09/17/smallbizpod-54-monday-17-september-2007/</guid><content:encoded xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><![CDATA[<div class="tweetmeme_button" style="margin-left: 3px;">
