<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp53.mp3">SmallBizPod #53</a>, the podcast for start-ups and entrepreneurs, includes an interview with a remarkable female entrepreneur, Jennifer Irvine of <a href="http://www.purepackage.com/">The Pure Package</a>.  There&#8217;s also a round up of comments from listeners and details of <a href="http://www.podcampuk.com">Podcamp UK</a>.</p>
<p>Right click <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp53.mp3">here</a> to download</p>
