izpod.co.uk)</dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 27 Jul 2007 11:12:25 PDT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/2007/07/27/smallbizpod-52-friday-27-july-2007/</guid><content:encoded xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><![CDATA[<div class="tweetmeme_button" style="margin-left: 3px;">
