<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp51.mp3">SmallBizPod #51</a>, the podcast for small business owners and entrepreneurs, includes an interview with Nigel Botterill, chief executive of <a href="http://www.thebestof.co.uk">thebestof.co.uk</a> about online business, franchising and how his local information site became one of the most visited UK websites.  There&#8217;s also the usual round up of comments from listeners and some summery electronica.</p>
<p>Right click <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp51.mp3">here</a> to download</p>
<p><strong>Click on the play button below to listen now</strong></p>
