<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp50.mp3">SmallBizPod #50</a>, the small business advice podcast, includes an interview with <a href="http://www.channel4.com/money/ontv/risking_it_all/presenter.html">Martin Webb</a>, serial entrepreneur, host of Channel 4&#8242;s Risking It All and author of <a href="http://www.amazon.co.uk/Make-Your-First-Million-Business/dp/1841127612/ref=pd_bowtega_1/203-9144522-1309503?ie=UTF8&amp;s=books&amp;qid=1182848387&amp;sr=1-1">Make Your First Million: Ditch the 9-5 and Start the Business of Your Dreams</a>.  There&#8217;s also the usual round up of comments and commentary from listeners.</p>
