 19 Jun 2007 10:55:39 PDT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/2007/06/19/smallbizpod-49-tuesday-19-june-2007/</guid><content:encoded xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><![CDATA[<div class="tweetmeme_button" style="margin-left: 3px;">
