<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp47.mp3">SmallBizPod #47</a>, the podcast for startups and entrepreneurs, returns to the subject of venture capital, how to pitch your business and how to secure funding.  The show features interviews with a student, business owner, teacher and sponsor all of whom took part in London Business School&#8217;s innovative <a href="http://www.london.edu/entrepreneurship/venturecapitalinvestmentcompetition.html">Venture Capital Investment Competition</a>.  Find out which team of trainee dragon&#8217;s won and which business was honoured to come top of the investment list.  The show also covers off the latest listener comments, news from the <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/blog">SmallBizPod blog</a> and a real gem of an electronica track.</p>
