<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp45.mp3">SmallBizPod #45</a>, the small business podcast, focuses on venture capital and female entrepreneurship.  The show includes a fascinating interview with Gita Patel of <a href="http://stargatecapital.co.uk">Stargate Capital</a> and provides an insight into how a VC thinks and how Gita came to set up the <a href="http://www.trapeziacapital.co.uk/">Trapezia fund</a> dedicated to supporting female high growth start-ups.  The show also includes audio comments, your chance to appear in a video podcast, more from the <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/blog">SmallBizPod blog</a>, advice for the wantrepreneur,  as well as the usual round up listener comments.</p>
