<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp43.mp3">SmallBizPod #43</a>, the podcast for entrepreneurs and start-ups, examines the European technology/web sector and the state of venture capital on the continent with <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alex_Vieux">Alex Vieux</a>, publisher of technology business magazine <a href="http://www.redherring.com/">Red Herring</a> which has recently announced its latest Europe 100 list.</p>
<p>Right click <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp43.mp3">here</a> to download</p>
