<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">•</span> 26:48 Comment on the blog from Rob <a href="http://main-spring.blogspot.com/">Smorfitt</a> re innovation &#8211; inspiration or necessity?</p>
<p>Features:</p>
