pod.co.uk (www.smallbizpod.co.uk)</dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2007 02:37:32 PST</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/2007/01/13/smallbizpod-37-wednesday-10-january-2007-with-correct-mp3-file/</guid><content:encoded xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><![CDATA[<div class="tweetmeme_button" style="margin-left: 3px;">
