<p>This week&#8217;s small business podcast, <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp34.mp3">SmallBizPod #34</a>, features an excellent interview by one of our listeners, <a href="http://blog.qubecommunications.com/">Juliette Prouse</a>, with <a href="http://www.torok.com">George Torok</a>, entrepreneur, best-selling Canadian author and marketing expert.  George and Juliette discuss how your business can get an unfair advantage over the competition and how you can build a personal brand.  There&#8217;s also a review of PodcastCon UK including live music from one of the bands that played as well as the usual round up of comments from listeners and the latest from the SmallBizPod <a href="http://www.frappr.com/smallbizpodcommunity">Frappr map</a> community.</p>
