<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">•</span> 00:00 Alex on what&#8217;s coming up in the show.</p>
<p>Features:</p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;">•</span> 01.55 <strong>Interview</strong> from SmallBizPod listener Juliette Prouse at <a href="http://blog.qubecommunications.com/">Qube</a> with George Torok, best selling Canadian business author and marketing guru.  George talks about how to get an unfair advantage over your competitors by applying systems and business principles that will take you beyond natural talent.  Juliette and George also talk about how to build a personal brand, &#8216;smell out&#8217; your best customers and how to overcome the emotional highs and lows of entrepreneurship.</p>
