allbizpod.co.uk)</dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jul 2006 09:00:45 PDT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/2006/07/06/smallbizpod-29-thursday-6-july-2006/</guid><content:encoded xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><![CDATA[<div class="tweetmeme_button" style="margin-left: 3px;">
