<p><a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp29.mp3">SmallBizPod #29</a>, the podcast for startups and small businesses, this week includes an interview from roving reporter Carl Barton who talks to coffee entrepreneur, Steve Leighton of <a href="http://www.hasbean.co.uk/">hasbean.co.uk</a> about the practicalities of importing goods, ethical business and his passion for coffee.  The show also includes a round up of listener comments including an audio comment from Fraser Edwards and highlights information and advice from Orange on how to enter this year&#8217;s <a title="The National Business Awards sponsored by Orange" href="http://www1.orange.co.uk/business/nba/?WT.mc_id=ora06080_un_03" target="_blank">National Business Awards</a>.</p>
