 29 Jun 2006 11:16:38 PDT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/2006/06/29/smallbizpod-28-thursday-29-june-2006/</guid><content:encoded xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><![CDATA[<div class="tweetmeme_button" style="margin-left: 3px;">
