<p>This week <a href="http://www.smallbizpod.co.uk/podcasts/Sbp26.mp3">SmallBizPod #26</a>, the podcast for entrepreneurs and small business owners, highlights advice on how to expand your business through international trade.  The show has an excellent interview with Simon Coyle a young Scottish entrepreneur whose designer chocolate brand, <a href="http://www.kshocolat.co.uk/">Kschocolat</a>, is now being sold across the globe.  There&#8217;s also a debate on what makes an entrepreneur and the usual round up of small business views and feedback from listeners around the world.</p>
