<p>This week SmallBizPod #24, the small buisness podcast for entrepreneurs and start-ups, includes a series of interviews and expert advice on how to recruit, motivate and manage staff and the thorny issue of employment legislation. Interviews include a conversation with Julia Scott, founder and managing director of <a href="http://www.baseconnections.co.uk/">Base Connections</a>, winner of European Call Centre of the Year, about her innovative approach to managing her people. There&#8217;s also a bumper round up of listeners&#8217; comments and frappr map feedback.</p>
